snippet.title: Warstride Challenges - Official E3 2021 Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam :  https://store.steampowered.com/app/1608470/Warstride_Challenges/
Dream Powered Games, a small 3 people indie dev team, is pleased to announce Warstride Challenges !
What if doom guy had a drunk one night stand with Super meatboy? Skill based Fast FPS, featuring challenging short levels and brutal gunfights. 
Find more at https://www.warcryfps.com/


Follow Warstride :
Twitter : https://twitter.com/warcrythegame

Discord : https://discord.gg/vYv4QhgE7y
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/DreamPoweredGames
